    Title: Sukhâvativyûha Sûtra
Title: Amida's Vow
Tags:
  - Invocation=The Glory of the Name
  - Life-Love=Charity=Cosmic Salvation
  - Discernment-Truth=The Eye Of Eternity-Supreme Center=The Ultimate Felicity
---
When I have attained Buddhahood, if all beings in the ten quarters, trusting
in me with the most sincere heart, should wish to be born in my Country,
and should utter my Name one to ten times, and if they should not be born
there, may I not attain Enlightenment.
